{"tid":1571091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反曱甴革命教戰手冊","createTime":"2019-09-15T10:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T10:28:45.000Z","uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce92e61e2b7a9b48958aa136cb7bf6a9366591d8","tid":1571091,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:26:19.000Z","msg":"發現陰招，幫手拆。<br />\n1.不排除最近多人被自殺都可能有關。<br />\n2.裡面提到&quot;香港警方的難處&quot;，其實，警方真的除了殺人都沒甚麼難處了。<br />\n3.大陸常用&quot;示威者鬧太久影響生活&quot;這個概念宣傳，我們也要反宣傳&quot;政府躲避市民訴求太久，影響民生&quot;<br />\n<br />\n//反曱甴革命教戰手冊<br />\nA.利用暴徒的telegram各群群組。<br />\n<a href=\"http://1.xn--t-i68aq1ol7gt4d02hw34aefgknhyrg.me/guardi......\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.xn--t-i68aq1ol7gt4d02hw34aefgknhyrg.me%2Fguardi......&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXebY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=f752e156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://1.xn--t-i68aq1ol7gt4d02hw34aefgknhyrg.me/guardi......</a> 記錄下來，列清單。<br />\n2.注意公開群組不要加入，查看其煽動鼓吹內容並截屏。<br />\n3.群組中可疑的telegram賬號和郵箱，用Google搜索查一遍，會另有收獲。有問題的內容記錄或匯總。群組內的link部分可順藤摸瓜。<br />\n4.從這些群組能查出曱甴補給站，休息站，就餐地點及相應的參與者支持者和同情者及相應的企業。<br />\n5.想辦法弄到家裏孩子或朋友的秘密群組內容。<br />\n6.把以上清單和截屏（注意包含網址或telegram群組名）<a href=\"http://提交到12339.gov.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%88%B012339.gov.cn&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXebY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=00052de9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">提交到12339.gov.cn</a>.請注意一定要提交國家安全局。香港警方有警方的難處。<br />\n大家都這樣做，很快曱甴革命就轉入地下，熄火。<br />\n這些家夥鬧時間太長了，影響我們工作和生活了。<br />\n其他待有時間再補充!歡迎轉發!//"},{"pid":"4e967d754af13b81e4eea548526681edf7203b18","tid":1571091,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4oZup8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4oZup8.jpg&h=22278f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXebY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=ab86c1a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXebY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=9e39e96b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"}]}